// Template for the maintainer's local secrets. To enable keyless swaps for end users:
//
//   1. Deploy the gateway (gateway/gateway.mjs) with ZEROX_KEY + APP_TOKEN set in its env.
//   2. cp Secrets.example.xcconfig Secrets.xcconfig
//   3. Paste the SAME value you used for the gateway's APP_TOKEN below.
//
// Secrets.xcconfig is gitignored, so the token never gets committed. The raw 0x API key is NEVER
// placed here — it belongs only in the gateway server's environment.
SEARXLY_GATEWAY_APP_TOKEN = paste-your-gateway-app-token-here
